      <title>荷兰政府降低所得税以提高购买力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/dutch-government-reduces-income-tax-to-boost-purchasing-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰政府表示，将降低所得税以提高购买力，并重新引入一些此前外籍人士享受的优惠政策，以改善商业环境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/dutch-government-reduces-income-tax-to-boost-purchasing-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 15:50:56 GMT</pubDate>
