    <item>
      <title>赞比亚矿业游说团体呼吁政府停止改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/zambia-mines-lobby-calls-on-government-to-halt-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赞比亚矿业商会表示，拟议的立法和政策改革对投资者的权利构成了“前所未有的威胁”，并将破坏该国将铜产量提高四倍的雄心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/zambia-mines-lobby-calls-on-government-to-halt-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 14:52:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰将向资金紧张的 Tennet 额外提供 190 亿欧元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/dutch-to-give-extra-19-billion-loan-to-capital-strapped-tennet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在与柏林就出售德国电网的谈判失败后，荷兰政府将向国有电网运营商 Tennet Holding BV 再提供 190 亿欧元（211 亿美元）贷款，满足其资本需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/dutch-to-give-extra-19-billion-loan-to-capital-strapped-tennet</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 14:47:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
